Employee Search React App
A simple React application for searching and displaying employee information.

🚀 Getting Started
To run the Employee Search React App locally, follow these steps:

Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/employee-search-react-app.git
Navigate to the project directory:

Install the dependencies:

npm install
Start the development server:

npm start
Open your browser and visit http://localhost:3000 to view the app.

💡 Usage
Enter a search query in the search bar to filter the employee list.
Click the search button or press Enter to initiate the search.
The search results will be displayed below the search bar.
Employee names and roles that match the search query will be highlighted.
The "Search Completed" label will appear once the search is finished.
🛠️ Technologies Used
React
Axios
CSS

Feel free to customize and enhance the application as per your requirements. Enjoy searching for employees with ease! 😊